cc46c94fe9c18","tid":100274,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>葉劉聽完一定又喊苦喊忽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e1cdf7bf7f1ba507ac032b18a406dee4403dc0","tid":100274,"uid":65473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"秋元真夏"},{"pid":"20144e458a5221f1fcf6e78fd6e122cd2cc1b977","tid":100274,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他指今年香港運勢有利女性候選人，林鄭較大機會當選，但轉運不代表香港前景好轉，有可能轉差，甚至今年內有動亂。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有危先有機，有機就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58643fef693ef7c8faa93aa61e109e9991b2e2c","tid":100274,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:41:26.000Z","msg":"一年前<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>李居明：梁振英似蔡英文有選舉運<br />\n<br />\n玄學家李居明上星期六在商台節目中，被問到梁振英能否連任，李居明雖說「咁尖銳嘅問題唔答！」但又笑稱「耍下太極」作出批算，指梁振英與台灣總統蔡英文的八字相當接近，現時62歲的梁振英，在59歲至69歲這10年，正好有選舉運。節目主持人再問，如果梁振英成功連任，又會否轉運，他就不置可否。<br />\n<br />\n蔡伯勵：梁振英屬馬「運勢大好」<br />\n<br />\n《信報》、《經濟日報》和《報條日報》昨日報道，曆法專家兼堪輿學家蔡伯勵星期三預測，明年屬馬最旺，「天德守命、喜上眉梢」，而梁振英正是馬年出生「運勢大好」，惟都沒有明確表示過梁振英當選機會。另外，至於盛傳即將宣布參選的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀屬虎，明年運勢「雖云小耗、尚有餘豐」，形勢似乎不錯。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a5e5ee129feab5c56278c49da76f8e6a31e51a8e","tid":100274,"uid":22919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"淋病都比記者撞"},{"pid":"f5d8be35e47fb01a88a5cf8bbc4946b4a4aa8212","tid":100274,"uid":51859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>他指另一參選人葉劉淑儀面相不是做特首，加上前年被麒麟撞倒，「佢3年衰運未過」。</blockquote><br />\n原來俾麒麟撞過咁大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要衰三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n選到特首對她也不一定是好事"},{"pid":"9ae851d543e29fcc5b2be10f96dc1153c52749ce","tid":100274,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要衰三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n選到特首對她也不一定是好事</blockquote><br />\n咁點解條臭西仲選到立法會"}]}